&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and own the facility’s preventive electrical maintenance plan, aligned to the 48-hour run / 12-hour maintenance cycle&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead or supervise all electrical and instrumentation work during planned maintenance windows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supervise and mentor on-shift Maintenance Technicians on electrical tasks and safety procedures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Diagnose and resolve electrical faults, control system errors, and instrumentation issues during production&lt;/li&gt;
