&lt;li&gt;Inbound Accuracy: Verify strict accuracy between delivery notes and physical stock received.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dispatch Accuracy: Ensure the correct batches and quantities are loaded for delivery.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bin Accuracy: Maintain precise records of where every item is located.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;FEFO/FIFO Compliance: Enforce 100% adherence to First-Expiry-First-Out (FEFO) and First-In-First-Out (FIFO) protocols to minimize expiry variance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Internal Transfers (IWT): Ensure IWT booking accuracy and dispatch accuracy for all stock moving in or out of your warehouse.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Warehouse Standards: Ensure proper stacking, hygiene, and temperature monitoring to prevent inventory&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;deterioration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;PQ Processes Execution&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute PQ Processes: Supervise the physical auditing, sorting, labelling and execution of PQ processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Documentation: Ensure PQ activities are accurately documented to satisfy Compliance and Government Relations requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
